Series II: Loose Framed and Unframed Photographs and Prints.

Loose photographs including: portraits of Elmer Holmes Bobst, ca.1915-1960; dedication of new Hoffman-LaRoche building, 1938; American Cancer Society Meeting with President Eisenhower, 1953; Cardiology Award Banquet, 1969; photographs of Elmer Holmes Bobst's 85th birthday at the White House with the Nixons.
